stories.title: Ponting: 'We were a bit rusty'
stories.subTitle: Zimbabwe v Australia, 1st ODI, Harare
stories.summary: Ricky Ponting has promised that Australia will turn in a far more clinical performance in the second and third one-dayers against Zimbabwe later this week

stories.title: Ponting and Martyn lead Australia's stroll to victory
stories.subTitle: Zimbabwe v Australia, 1st ODI, Harare
stories.summary: Although they probably had to work harder than they expected, in the end Australia cantered to victory over Zimbabwe by seven wickets in the first match of this rearranged one-day series at the Harare Sports Club
